data.description: MOVE IN READY IN YORKTOWN! Nestled in the quiet neighborhood of Harwood Heights, this home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, nearly 2400 square feet and an oversized kitchen w/ all of the storage you're looking for. The relaxing den with fireplace sits just below the bonus room over the garage. Outside you can relax or entertain on the oversized deck overlooking the fenced backyard that's great for kids, pets, or any outside hobbies. Newer HVAC (approx. 2021), generator hookup, updated electrical panel, and dehumidifier in the crawl (approx. 2020) offer peace of mind. Come and see for yourself and let's turn this house into a home!
